reviewText:
Sadly this game is not recomended after you play great quality ARPG.

In short: only buy if you don`t mind to play a generic MMO style punched into a single player game.

Positives:
+ Interesting visual alert when your heath is low;
+ Music and Blind Guardian (their music blends with the animus" of ARPG);
+ Unique characters to play

date:
 including good and evil oriented;
+ Nice graphics and runs in 2560 x 1080 (to people with ultra-wide);
+ They tried to make a funny game.

Negatives:
- Huge map plagued with non stop monsters spawn (rats...kobolts);
- Repetitive quests: it`s 500 of boredom;
- No sense of real progression;
- Weak story;
- At glance
